Python Hyves API.

requirements:
 * python >= 2.5
 * oauth >= 1.0
 * enum >= 0.4

Although lower versions might work, they have not been tested.

comm.py / HyvesAPIComm:
 * handle oAuth
 * handle server exceptions (todo)
 * handle minimal parameters (ha_version, ha_fancylayout, ha_format)

hyvesapi.py / HyvesAPIProxy
 * convert python method calls to hyves API requests
 * set default ha_responsefields when loading aggressively

demo.py contains a small demonstation
